{"tid":2292102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【缺德阿伯】茶樓阿伯直接茶壺對嘴飲茶恐播毒　網民憂：間間酒樓都唔洗茶壺","createTime":"2020-11-19T08:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T12:30:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed0118f121ba753e49590f57a739482a2eae809","tid":2292102,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:47:28.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情持續更應保持衛生！有網民在茶樓目擊一名阿伯飲茶時，直接在茶壺嘴飲茶，令人擔心衛生問題。<br />\n<br />\n網民於Facebook群組「秀茂坪吹水區」圖文並茂發帖，指自己陪家中老人家飲茶時，驚見一名阿伯直接在茶壺嘴飲茶，直斥「離晒大譜，點可能冇菌啊。」<br />\n<br />\n她指日後飲茶是否需要出動私家茶壺，亦呼籲大家於自己屋村飲茶時，都要記得洗乾淨茶壺，會更安全。<br />\n<br />\n一眾網民見到阿伯的離譜行為，紛紛指責阿伯無衛生常識、無公德心：「隔夜飯都嘔埋出嚟」、「個壺冇洗就真係大鑊，想嘔」、「離曬譜！！！ 太邋遢啦，恐怖呀！」。<br />\n<br />\n亦有很多網民指，茶樓基本上不會徹底清洗茶壺：「間間酒樓都唔洗茶壺㗎喎，上一張枱用完下一張枱就用」、「個壺倒左d茶，換d新茶熱水，當唔當洗左？」、「沖下就算，邊會洗，而且無咩人洗個嘴。」<br />\n<br />\n同時不少網民也分享自己的經歷，見過「有大叔將食完的骨頭殘渣，掉落茶壺裏面」、「曾經見過有人吐痰落去茶壺」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2806812/125808760_10207880050875802_8115130860377208083_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2806812%2F125808760_10207880050875802_8115130860377208083_n_1024.jpg&h=322da500&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8e20086ee4b1fc2e6fca30a98625c5915c85710","tid":2292102,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:14:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e09c733e9a969e8808d458d83c1e439e86ea194c","tid":2292102,"uid":95494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"唔熱既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d6f5a97df20757b0929d9ecd1724e14a254d3c","tid":2292102,"uid":19648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"口渴呀屌"},{"pid":"a33ea8254bccf32b3a359be298d3db732d0fe734","tid":2292102,"uid":324041,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"唉！之所以香港d酒樓茶樓點解會越做越頹後生仔少幫襯，咪多得呢d核突廢老囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f134339a064c419bbc2b1f7461435ec0f0e583b","tid":2292102,"uid":5218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野要遮住呢 d 廢老樣？"},{"pid":"e84a839f1c6ea8c4d908450a55035e72350823f7","tid":2292102,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f134339a064c419bbc2b1f7461435ec0f0e583b","tid":2292102,"uid":5218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野要遮住呢 d 廢老樣？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"原圖係咁"},{"pid":"e64c61d392664331ed7ccab946142046c50a2381","tid":2292102,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"係咪老懵董嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a372ac5cde4af5e1debac8b997a72496a4378fd","tid":2292102,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ffa12f777a93dbd0f8d9f4306cf06c84a49832","tid":2292102,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"5fac40f2b6a398feeb45ebc1131299176cf45795","tid":2292102,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"酒樓廢老集中地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32e394ac1ba419a3deb06b2b1d460f1b0666f59","tid":2292102,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/